.container
	h1 Dialog made easy
	button.btn.btn-primary((click)="open()") Click me!!!

	div.alert.alert-info(*ngIf="dialogRes")
		p(*ngIf="dialogRes.dismiss") You dismissed dialog
		p(*ngIf="dialogRes.close") You closed dialog, with this data:
		pre(*ngIf="dialogResData")
			| {{ dialogResData | json }}

	button.btn.btn-danger((click)="confirm()") Delete
	.alert.alert-danger(*ngIf="confirmed")
		| We are processing you request

